Package com.marklogic.semantics.jena.engine

Jena extensions that wire MarkLogic functionality into Jena's query processing and graph manipulation APIs.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MarkLogicQueryEngine
    Implements a hook into the Jena query execution framework for working with MarkLogic.
    MarkLogicQueryEngine.MarkLogicQueryEngineFactory
    For internal use.
    MarkLogicUpdateEngine
    Provides a connection between Jena's update mechanism and SPARQL UPDATE on MarkLogic.
    MarkLogicUpdateEngine.MarkLogicUpdateEngineFactory
    Creates the UpdateEngine for integration into Jena.
